---
// Identity hero. Left column: eyebrow, display headline, mono body.
// Right column: Sync stat tile (commits across accounts).
---

<section
  id="main"
  class="container-wide identity-section"
  style="position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; gap: 56px; flex-wrap: wrap;"
>
  <div
    style="max-width: 820px; flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;"
  >
    <div
      class="reveal"
      style="--reveal-delay: 0ms; display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 12px;"
    >
      <span
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 9999px; background: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0;"
      ></span>
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted);"
      >
        Now
      </span>
    </div>

    <h1
      class="reveal hero-h1"
      style="--reveal-delay: 100ms; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.025em; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 0;"
    >
      Hey. I'm Jon.<br />I ideate, build and ship rad things.
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mono reveal"
      style="--reveal-delay: 200ms; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 400; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.025em; line-height: 19.8px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); max-width: 640px; margin: 0;"
    >
      Rethinking how we learn online. Design + code + AI agents. Vibe-coding daily from Austin. Below: what I touched today, live, not curated.
    </p>
  </div>

  <aside
    aria-label="Sync stats"
    class="reveal sync-tile"
    style="--reveal-delay: 300ms; flex-shrink: 0; background: var(--color-bg-elevated); border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline); padding: 24px 26px; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 106, 61, 0.08);"
  >
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px;">
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted);"
      >
        Sync
      </span>
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 400; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent);"
      >
        ● Live · 4m ago
      </span>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: baseline; gap: 10px; margin-top: 16px;">
      <span
        data-counter="1284"
        aria-label="1,284 commits"
        style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 400; font-size: 56px; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1; color: var(--color-fg); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; display: inline-block; min-width: 5ch;"
      >
        0
      </span>
      <span
        style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 400; font-size: 11px; color: var(--color-accent);"
      >
        +22%
      </span>
    </div>

    <p
      style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 400; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 16px; color: var(--color-muted); margin: 14px 0 0 0;"
    >
      Commits · 26w · 2 accounts · 7 branches
    </p>
  </aside>
</section>

<style>
  .identity-section {
    padding: 80px 48px 56px;
  }
  .hero-h1 {
    font-size: 76px;
    line-height: 80px;
  }
  .sync-tile {
    width: 280px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .identity-section {
      padding: 56px 32px 40px;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: 56px;
      line-height: 60px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .identity-section {
      padding: 40px 20px 32px;
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      line-height: 44px;
    }
    .sync-tile {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
